intent.user_query: What is the customer acquisition rate per month?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT CAST(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM RegistrationDate) AS VARCHAR(4)) || '-' || CAST(EXTRACT(MONTH FROM RegistrationDate) AS VARCHAR(2)) AS RegistrationMonth, COUNT(*) AS NewCustomers FROM fitness_db.Customers GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT CAST(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM RegistrationDate) AS VARCHAR(4)) || '-' || CAST(EXTRACT(MONTH FROM RegistrationDate) AS VARCHAR(2)) AS RegistrationMonth, COUNT(*) AS NewCustomers FROM fitness_db.Customers GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
